---
title: Sticky Sriracha Cauliflower with Hoisin Noodles, Mangetout and Sesame
description: Our Sticky Sriracha Cauliflower is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W35_UK_V15315-4_Main_low-78cdedcd.jpg
